headline: 5 Must-Read Analyst Questions From Datadog’s Q3 Earnings Call
summary: Datadog’s third quarter was marked by broad-based customer adoption and significant expansion in both AI and non-AI segments, contributing to a positive market reaction. Management highlighted accelerating usage growth among existing customers, with CEO Olivier Pomel noting, “Sequential usage growth for non-AI existing customers was the highest we have seen going back 12 quarters.” The company recorded notable wins across large enterprises and saw its digital experience and security product suit
